'''Argigi''' neɣ '''Targagayt''' d awliwel [[tigawt tarmerrit|armerri]] asnagaran yettmag-d s usrag (s sebba) n unɣas n [[tamaẓwalt|tmaẓwalin]], akken i d-yettili deg-s usunfu d umussu n tiddit d tuɣalin deg kra n wegmam n [[tafekka|tfekka]] neɣ ugar.

Argigi d awliwel imezdi yakk gar n iwliwlen irmerriyen, yezmer ad yeglu s yisemda ɣef yifassen d yiɣallen d wallen d wudem d uqerru yakk d yimeslan. Maca amur ameqran seg wergigi i d-yettilin yettwaẓray deg yifassen. Ma ɣer kra n yimdanen, argigi yettumeggez d [[asken]] neɣ yemmal-d kra n wuguren deg [[anagraw anesur|wunagraw ansur]].

